== B) SEAM AUDIT (conservative overlap-bounded reconciliation) ==

[washington_01] 3 segs, assembled 191w, assembled-loop: none
  seam seg0->seg1 | exact_overlap_trim | drop-curr 4tok ""On the other hand,"
  seam seg1->seg2 | FUZZY_ANCHOR_SPLICE anchor="his own deficiencies."" | drop-prev 1tok "[BLANK_AUDIO]" | drop-curr 3tok "his own deficiencies."
